				"string" : "Short answer: **Yes ‚Äî the SOM‚Äôs reference vectors behave very much like the ‚Äúinner models‚Äù in Br√•ten‚Äôs *beteiligte Spiegelung* (participatory mirror-matching).**\nBut with an important precision: **they are models *without intentionality* ‚Äî structural mirrors, not social ones.** [chatgpt](https://chatgpt.com/g/g-p-691997577a78819194cd62664eb19c31-som/c/691cf32a-d904-832c-9b20-aff7e0db31da)\n\nBelow is the clear mapping.\n"
