				"string" : "# ‚úî Br√•ten: ‚ÄúBeteiligte Spiegelung‚Äù ‚Äî what it is\n\nBr√•ten‚Äôs concept refers to:\n\n* a system that **carries an internal model** of its interaction partner,\n* updates this model in response to interaction,\n* and uses it to regulate its own behavior.\n\nIt‚Äôs a *participatory*, *mutual*, *internalized* mirroring.\nNot just reflection ‚Äî but *co-constitution via interaction*.\n\nKey ingredients:\n\n1. **Alter-model**\n   The system maintains an internal representation of the Other.\n\n2. **Self‚Äìother coupling**\n   Updates occur through reciprocal exchange.\n\n3. **Topological coherence**\n   The system organizes internal models in a structured relational space.\n"
