				"string" : "---\n\n# ‚úî Where the analogy *breaks* (important)\n\nBr√•ten‚Äôs model involves:\n\n* intentionality\n* coordination with an ‚Äúalter‚Äù\n* mutual regulation\n* embodied subjectivity\n\nSOM has:\n\n* no agency\n* no bidirectional modelling (data does not adapt to SOM)\n* no intentional coupling\n\nSo the analogy is structural, not phenomenological.\n\nStill, as a **cognitive architecture metaphor** the alignment is excellent.\n"
